commit.title: cloudapi/v2: recover from panics in serializeManifest
commit.message:
cloudapi/v2: recover from panics in serializeManifest

Certain code paths result in a panic from images. While this should be
avoided in images, let's make the manifest generation job slightly more
robust by recovering from these panics. Currently these panics crash the
container and force a restart, this could impact other manifest jobs on
the same pod.

user.name: Ondřej Budai
user.bio: Principal Software Engineer @ Image Builder, Red Hat

Fixes the following error:
```
Failed to load ["/etc/vector/vector.yaml"]
x More than one component with name "executor" (source, sink).
x Input "executor" for sink "executor" doesn't match any components.
```
